ops::bit::BitAnd::bitand.doc:
Performs the `&` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true & false, false);
assert_eq!(true & true, true);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 1u8, 1);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 2u8, 0);
```

